ROW.ENT:
First-Class Pilot
Master, Mate, or Master, Mate (Pilot) of towing vessels may serve as pilot if he or she:

1. Is at least 21 years old;

2. Has an annual physical exam;

3. Maintains current knowledge of the waters to be navigated;1 and

4. Has at least 6 months' service in the deck department on towing vessels engaged in towing
